Euripid

This project may bundle the k6 binary (bin/k6.exe) for Windows zero-install
convenience. k6 is licensed under the GNU Affero General Public License v3.0
and is copyright Grafana Labs and contributors. The bundled binary is
unmodified. Source: https://github.com/grafana/k6

Euripid scenarios load the following third-party k6 modules at runtime via
URL imports. These are not redistributed in this repository:

  - k6-reporter (benc-uk)        MIT
    https://github.com/benc-uk/k6-reporter
  - k6 jslib papaparse           MIT
    https://github.com/grafana/jslib.k6.io
  - k6 jslib k6-summary          MIT
    https://github.com/grafana/jslib.k6.io

All three are imported by version-pinned URL (papaparse 5.1.1, k6-summary
0.0.2, k6-reporter 3.0.4). Full vendoring (local copies) is planned for v1.1.
